author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Five9 Reports Q1 Non-GAAP Earnings Per Share $0.08
text:
May 1 (Reuters) - Five9 Inc:
* FIVE9 REPORTS FIRST QUARTER REVENUE GROWTH OF 25% TO A RECORD $58.9 MILLION
* Q1 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.08
* Q1 REVENUE $58.9 MILLION VERSUS I/B/E/S VIEW $55.1 MILLION
* Q1 GAAP LOSS PER SHARE $0.01 * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.03 — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* SEES Q2 2018 GAAP LOSS PER BASIC SHARE $0.08 TO $0.10 * SEES Q2 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.03 TO $0.04
* SEES FY 2018 REVENUE $235.8 MILLION TO $238.8 MILLION * SEES FY 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.25 TO $0.30
* SEES FY 2018 GAAP LOSS PER BASIC EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.17 TO $0.22
* FY2018 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.23, REVENUE VIEW $232.9 MILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q2 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.04, REVENUE VIEW $55.5 MILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
